tagline: The Seattle Student Chapter of the Acoustical Society of America
body:
### Welcome to the online home of SSCASA.


### General Meeting November 6th
Interested in acoustics? Do you use acoustics in your work? Do you want to meet with other ASA student members here at UW? Then join us for the first general meeting of the newly minted SSCASA. 

Get in on the ground floor as we plan our activities for the year 2013/2014!

 

New to SSCASA?

We’ll tell you what we’re all about at this meeting.

Our By Laws and Charter are available here:
By-Laws
Charter

Membership forms will be available at the meeting. Membership is free!

Beer and snacks will be provided.
